Catherine C. MASTO, Attorney General of Nevada, et al., petitioners,
v.
Dennis K. KIEREN, Jr. No. 13-1529 R46-023. Supreme Court of the United States Aug. 6, 2014.

Opinion *1152The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.
